tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits except for a mildly decreased HbA1c, which may reflect recent hypoglycemia, anemia, or altered red cell turnover. Renal function, electrolytes, and glucose are normal. No acute laboratory abnormalities detected; clinical correlation for low HbA1c is recommended.
